scene.message:
Maki's Mom: Oh...{wait_fr:32}{nl}
where am I...?{wait_fr:32}{nl}
Isn't this the nurse's office?{waitkey}{clearbox}My, it's the haunted manor.{nl}
I was just dreaming{nl}
of this very place.{waitkey}{ret}

Mark: There's no Sonomura's{nl}
mom in this world...{waitkey}{clearbox}...She's the real thing!{nl}
But why is she here...{wait_fr:32}{nl}
Ma'am, are you okay?{waitkey}{ret}

Maki's Mom: Yes, I'm fine...{waitkey}When Maki was small, she'd{nl}
often get lost in this manor,{nl}
so I'd come searching.{nl}
I was dreaming of those days.{waitkey}{clearbox}As I wandered these{nl}
vast halls all alone,{nl}
I heard Maki calling out...{waitkey}...and after that,{nl}
I don't remember a thing.{waitkey}{ret}

Maki: Um, ma'am...{nl}
I'm really{nl}
not your child.{waitkey}{ret}

Maki's Mom: I see...{wait_fr:32}{nl}
You're the Maki{nl}
of this world.{waitkey}{clearbox}But I wonder why I'm{nl}
nowhere to be found{nl}
in this world...{waitkey}{ret}

Mark: Ma'am, we've got{nl}
to go after{nl}
Kandori.{waitkey}{ret}

Maki's Mom: This dimension{nl}
gate is in a very{nl}
unstable state.{waitkey}{clearbox}Someone must stay here{nl}
to work the machine.{waitkey}{ret}

Maki: Someone has to{nl}
stay behind?{nl}
No! We can't leave{nl}
anyone behind!{waitkey}{ret}

Maki's Mom: I'll do it!{nl}
I'll keep the gate stable,{nl}
so don't worry, off you go.{waitkey}{clearbox}If you'd come back for me{nl}
once it's all over,{nl}
I'd be so happy.{waitkey}{ret}

Maki: I don't have a{nl}
mother of my own,{waitkey}{clearbox}but if I had a kind{nl}
mom like you,{wait_fr:32}{nl}
I'd have been so glad...{waitkey}{ret}

Maki: Once we beat Kandori,{nl}
I'll be sure to find your{nl}
own little Maki, too!{waitkey}{ret}

Maki's Mom: ...{wait_fr:16}...{wait_fr:16}...{wait_fr:16}{nl}
Yes, that's right.{wait_fr:64}{nl}
Thank you...{waitkey}{ret}

Maki's Mom: Off you go,{nl}
everyone!{nl}
Do take care!{waitkey}{ret}
